cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: "taxcord – a tool to condense NCBI BLAST hits into per-OTU lineages, refine them with GBIF/BOLD occurrences, and reconcile them with BOLD into a consensus"
abstract: >-
  A tool that condenses NCBI BLAST hits into one confident lineage
  per OTU, refines them with GBIF/BOLD occurrence counts for one or more chosen
  countries, and reconciles NCBI and BOLD data into a consensus.
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Sara
    family-names: Sampaio
